Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝王多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、火美子和武一郎師傅\N一邊和多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊以第七界層為目標前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第四界層得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能令炎熱的第三界層\N回復原狀的極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全地把它交還了亞撒姆像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令第三界層\N回復原來的和平世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,今次到第四界層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為把灼熱之劍交還胡娜拉像\N我們上了第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.87,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九話\N龍神丸飛了,飛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是雪啊!雪啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷!…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,快點出去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這裏太冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪之國…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如傳聞一樣冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,我不是皮草啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你,在下最怕冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅\N你不是說過最怕熱的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.92,0:03:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,冷也不行\N我對溫度太敏感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好噁心\N不要用你的巨臉貼著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很巨大,真抱歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起此事,還是快點\N把灼熱之劍交還胡娜拉像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,趕快吧,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是頸巾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這差勁的品味是什麼?\N多多路高士蒙也是個蠢材吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別投訴了\N只要打倒那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便要和這噁心的地說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥,讓那個叫渡的小鬼\N知道我們的可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他享受盡痛苦\N才送他進地獄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼻子沒有了,鼻子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘惡鳥,去追他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘兄弟大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等等,請問你們去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.05,0:04:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要用屁股向著我說話\N我們現在去收拾渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請再多給我一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屁股和頭也一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你們的福\N今次一定可以收拾渡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以暫時請你們\N留多這裏一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高士蒙\N我最討厭做無謂的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以這人頭擔保\N你不是無謂的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是無謂之極啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那信任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能信任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能、不能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來只有令你們信任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的客人有100人\N小學3年平成八年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧林匹克是第41屆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短槍郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假扮他人仍家常便飯\N不論何時也能自由變身的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.20,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芋川短槍郎,登場!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah!  很多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The great super易容師\N短槍郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我應該說超級偉大易容師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實這傢伙很怕洋文字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洋文字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說…hamburg
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等等\N如果他扮成雪便能接近渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也能搶奪灼熱之劍\N當然刺殺的準備也萬全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位只要在此\N一邊吃一邊等便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流水拉麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.10,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這面是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以飛象過河啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…,胡娜拉像在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過了那座山便到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便到了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何可以把這麼大工夫的事\N說得這麼輕鬆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,聽到幻覺了\N這樣的地方沒可能有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是幻覺!是幻覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是渡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪\N是渡的相識嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見到你太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真生外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這便是灼熱之劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看,讓我看,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.54,0:07:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起這個\N還是趕快去野野神殿吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大風雪也弱下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢\N但是胡娜拉像又再移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.70,0:07:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大風雪停了真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼\N你會有這麼大的床單?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可愛的女孩呢\N一點點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要過這吊橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這條橋\N不是已冰封了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.63,0:08:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這樣\N有一點衝擊也會碎散呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這樣也非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,拿著兩把劍會很重吧\N我替你拿一把吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重少少沒問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.72,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點…\N我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不要跳啊\N但是我很難活動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險,是冰雹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已到地獄了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪\N就算只有渡和火美子也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說這些好聽話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是Oh my god呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\N我…只是有點慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條橋已完了\N那之後怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖…雖然有點遠\N走別的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我不是想懷疑你的朋友\N但是太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會?\N你有什麼根據嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她雖然說胡娜拉像移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她現在和亞撒姆重聚中\N沒可能會動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我卻不能說一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊\N這樣不是不能成為理由吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是這是同樣是間諜的直覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!\N鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,你太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知我說得太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在把灼熱之劍\N交還胡娜拉像要緊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,相信曾經出賣他的人\N始終是沒可能的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等等,你是雪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是渡的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡在哪裏?\N他一直也不來令我很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,你可以和我一起來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要繞到哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很遠呢\N離山已這麼遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題,只差少少便到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點想法子的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如放下劍休息一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是呢\N師傅,休息一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣吧\N我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只對吃有興趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜歡吃東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是老實的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想吃ice-cream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ice-cream嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼冷\N我不想想起ice-cream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想吃curry rice呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下想喝熱熱的cream soup呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是ice-cream了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要vanilla和chocolate味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,punt cake也不錯呢\N要放很多cheese
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙fish的話會很暖呢\N但這裏沒可能吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很想吃呢\N差不多走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?怎麼了?雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒…倒是趕快行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N這樣再去一次山谷那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等啊\N古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了\N原來雪是有孿生姐妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,那傢伙是假扮的雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過分\N那邊才是假扮的,對吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒你辦法\N她是你朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,誰才是真的呢?\N歡迎真人到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼真的雪是誰呢?\N那現在由她的朋友問問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.98,0:14:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真是雪\N應該是拿著火龍之鱗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定是綠色那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,雪小姐\N準備好鱗片了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼現在來了\N誰才是真的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有請…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越來越令我不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N沒有其他方法可以分辨嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.17,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,雪受傷的時候\N我曾幫她塗藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.75,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,留有傷痕的\N便是真正的小雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,先看這邊的小雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪處?\N師傅,不用這麼近也看見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這種事不搞清楚不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.61,0:15:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有錯了,好\N跟著到那邊的小雪給我看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?不可以看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.63,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有傷痕表示你是假的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然這樣,和我想的一樣呢\N假的雪…是你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?有傷痕的是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,替雪塗的藥\N是火美子處取來的萬能藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這藥是可以令傷痕也消失的\N對吧,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對\N不愧是渡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你們看穿了真厲害\N我是創界山第一易容師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芋川短槍郎就是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.23,0:16:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便攻過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,雪,你拿著這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光頭,光頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!\N古拿瑪,雪小姐拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,是陷阱啊,快回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能來到這裏是你運氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但之後便要你\N試試我的厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷神火炎劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,電話…\N那邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰-神-丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,戰神丸?\N在午飯前打給你真不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋風飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N用飛龍拳讓那傢伙停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.95,0:18:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,飛龍拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,讓在下收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊交給你了,魔幻怪光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,渡,雪她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,去救雪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你去的,看招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?你無從入手吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這邊交給空神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古拿瑪嗎?\N看來你已加入了他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是龍神丸飛起了一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害\N是龍神丸和空神丸的合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸在空中飛翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,空神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣了,渡\N放低雪之後,就這樣開戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,去了哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,旋風風彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,用下一招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天空龍牙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.99,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,短槍郎那個蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等著你的屁股人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點用也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘兄弟大人,請原諒我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒法子吧,就這樣撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然胡娜拉像\N是沒有移動過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.87,0:21:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,我沒有聽你說話\N真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理它吧,已過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,千人僊人在等著\N快點去野野神殿吧,快點!

